ÐžÑ†ÐµÐ½ÐºÐ°: 9.0 Ð±Ð°Ð»Ð»Ð¾Ð² | Deus Ex was mostly fantastic! The game has you play as Adam Jensen, a guy who definitely didn't ask for this.

The controls and the movement and the styling of the game is all superb; perhaps a little lacking on the "generic bad guys standing in the halls" graphics, but what else is new. 

The gameplay is fun and intuitive, and provides a huge, huge wealth of story. Which, is what the game mainly comprises of. If you want an all-action shooty game, you'll have an "okay" time in Deus Ex. If you want an enthralling, twisty "ohmigoshnohedidnt" story, with tonnes of little snippets and extras to unlock ingame then this is the game for you.

Loads of fun, loved every minute!

